data.description: Home for the holidays in this stunning split floor plan nestled in River Birch Place featuring private playground. This home exudes charm and has been thoughtfully updated to offer modern comfort and style. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by fresh interior paint & flex room. The updated front door sets the tone for what awaits inside. Updated Lighting and ceiling fans. As you enter the great room, you'll immediately notice the gas start fireplace and open floor plan.  The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts beautiful granite countertops, breakfast bar, working island perfect space for the chef. Pantry and newer stainless dishwasher, microwave and 5 burner gas range. The covered patio faces mature trees and no neighbors directly behind. Spacious bedrooms and closets, primary bedroom has double vanity, jetted tub & shower. High tray and vaulted ceilings throughout. HVAC replaced 2023. Bonus pantry off the laundry and floored attic in garage for organizing and storage.
